snippet.title: BOMBFEST - War on the Desktop | PC and Consoles
snippet.description:
BOMBFEST is explosive party-game fun for up to four players! Blow your enemies away and be the last toy standing, but don't get caught in a chain reaction of explosions! Buy it today! Follow us at www.playbombfest.com

BOMBFEST: @playbombfest www.playbombfest.com
Whitethorn Digital: @whitethorngames www.whitethorndigital.com
Microsoft Store: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/bombfest/9n79mg04bvq1?activetab=pivot:overviewtab
Nintendo Store: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/bombfest-switch
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/729640/BOMBFEST/
